Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一等 要按照順序來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對不起 已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像是倒映著天空的湖一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真藍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸 不需要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼是疑問句呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不要客氣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙也很高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也非常高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}非常棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這首曲子被選為自由曲我感到非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fs35\an7}註：參賽曲目分為指定曲和自由曲。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙以前知道這首曲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最近在比賽中非常有人氣的卯田小姐製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}卯田小姐 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個我從圖書館借過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小時候有讀過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}講的是一個名叫莉茲的孤獨女孩的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}從來都是孤單一人的莉茲的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}陌生的少女到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿~ 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我叫傘木希美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要不要一起進入吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}兩人變得非常要好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就這樣開始一起居住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是最後兩個人分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}來到莉茲身旁的少女其實是青鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}從莉茲身旁飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像就是這樣的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像有點像我們的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼回…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是分開之類的真讓人悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故事還是要Happy End才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要不稍微試著吹一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獨奏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}第三樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}出於愛的決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}開頭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}音高是有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是還有很長一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真想快點在正式比賽上吹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美喜歡練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喜歡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這首曲子也?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真期待正式比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明是星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}佩服佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}痛~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 是部長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你分明是看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}稍微有點睡糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家真是早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們也足夠早了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已經來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我先去分組練習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}學姐吃軟糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 要吃要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等等 我是對學姐說的欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我沒吃早餐就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒吃就來會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早餐吃了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}平常的吐司 起司之類的 蛋之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}飯隨便搭點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}湯泡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這根本沒辦法吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完全沒辦法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蕾實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}法式吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真想快點在正式比賽中吹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正式比賽什麼的永遠都不要來才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安 阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早安 莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲 今天就結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天見 阿爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}向所有的糧食…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}暴風雨已經結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昨天的暴風雨就像假的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}藍色的… 女孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天的練習到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天主要以課題曲為中心練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天的預定是以莉茲為中心來練習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請為此做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}部長有什麼要說的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就如同大家一起決定的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今年的目標是在全國大賽上拿到金獎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這之後雖然有試音會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不論是被選上的成員
