Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}仍舊是團隊的成員 這點不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家互相支持
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}建立一個最強的北宇治吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要說的就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個好可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的欸 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希學姐的拋光布也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希學姐的叫法也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好可愛 希學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對你們來說可愛就那麼需要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}當然需要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們真是合拍呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那邊一直都很熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就像小鳥們的聚會一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下次要跟低音管部分的人辦一個雙簧樂器聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不對 反正也就是回家路上一起喝個下午茶之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧冢學姐也一起來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}難得雙簧樂器也就只有四個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是 這樣嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 霙辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天回家路上要跟我的聲部的人一起去家庭餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個… 早上的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是呢 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美 你喜歡這個故事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}結尾雖然有點悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 這就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}總之就是Double Lou Reed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fs35\an7}註：組合了雙簧樂器（Double Reed）和著名歌手婁·里德（Lou Reed）的冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 鎧冢學姐 你辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}學姐 好冷淡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我相信 我記得你是雙簧管的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧…不對 我是劍崎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧的… 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有關鎧冢學姐的事 想要跟你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個…學姐你跟鎧冢學姐關係很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是這麼覺得的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以想跟你請教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 那個 我好像跟鎧冢學姐相處的不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即使向她搭話也不怎麼回應我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算跟她對話了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感覺她也沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}難不成我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被討厭了嗎?我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙的話 稍微有點不可思議的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大概 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是劍崎 還有 是梨梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想梨梨花沒有被討厭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 這是謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯? 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}便利商店買的水煮蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.93,0:24:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已經調過味了 很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.82,0:24:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.83,0:24:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.17,0:24:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.59,0:24:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你變得這麼有精神 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.90,0:25:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲的手帕…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.75,0:25:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然有這麼多的麵包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.13,0:25:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.79,0:25:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.97,0:25:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個也可以摘嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.60,0:25:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.53,0:26:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要嚐嚐看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.12,0:26:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.71,0:26:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.22,0:26:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是從哪裡來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.65,0:26:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.03,0:26:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過我見過了很多的城鎮跟森林
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.03,0:26:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼會來到這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.04,0:26:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為莉茲是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想跟莉茲一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.51,0:27:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.85,0:27:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.98,0:27:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜託了 待在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.61,0:27:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}永遠 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.53,0:27:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}待在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.24,0:27:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到離校的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.08,0:27:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還請速速離校
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.66,0:27:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放學的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.79,0:27:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.55,0:27:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要鎖門了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.22,0:27:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.07,0:27:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.58,0:27:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}作業做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.89,0:27:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.10,0:27:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.56,0:27:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}超級努力 超帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.90,0:27:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}運動也很擅長 哪裡都很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.53,0:28:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是 皋月的…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.70,0:28:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「最喜歡了」的擁抱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.37,0:28:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她們是從南中畢業的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.70,0:28:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中學的時候流行過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.75,0:28:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是敢做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.67,0:28:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一邊相互說著喜歡的地方 一邊擁抱對方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.13,0:28:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我一直只是旁觀著
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.13,0:28:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}從來沒有做過
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.18,0:28:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.14,0:28:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.01,0:28:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}開玩笑的 生厭了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.15,0:28:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.11,0:28:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.27,0:28:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.37,0:28:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.99,0:28:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.41,0:28:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}早呀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.63,0:28:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.30,0:29:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.84,0:29:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}耶~
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.80,0:29:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.43,0:29:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}夏紀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.77,0:29:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.94,0:29:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧冢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.73,0:29:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}志願調查表
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.86,0:29:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你除了名字什麼都沒寫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.90,0:29:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下週為止 好好地寫完交上來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.62,0:29:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.24,0:29:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}比方說 像2與3 4與5這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.87,0:29:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}公約數除了1以外就沒有了的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.96,0:29:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就叫做互質
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.89,0:29:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}夏紀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.77,0:30:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 交換
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.28,0:30:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙 該交換了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.49,0:30:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.36,0:30:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不上場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.45,0:30:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}額 真是沒辦法吶
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.33,0:30:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.18,0:30:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被人家說「可愛」了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.85,0:30:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是同班的生物研究會的男生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.48,0:30:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好厲害啊 在什麼情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.53,0:30:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在討論早餐吃什麼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.99,0:30:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.82,0:30:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「法式吐司」之後
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.28,0:30:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 抄襲
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.04,0:30:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那不是蕾實的答案嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.83,0:30:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.16,0:30:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.37,0:31:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.17,0:31:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希學姐有過約會的經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.68,0:31:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}河豚~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.33,0:32:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}馬上就試音會了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.16,0:33:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.70,0:33:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}長笛獨奏應該是希學姐上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.50,0:33:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 畢竟吹得那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.74,0:33:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}（加油~）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.12,0:33:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快看 莉茲 月亮升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.24,0:33:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.37,0:33:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天也該會是晴天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.62,0:33:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.29,0:33:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天能和莉茲好好玩耍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.01,0:33:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.01,0:34:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也是 晚安 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.85,0:34:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明天見~
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.08,0:35:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再過一段時間就要變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.00,0:35:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 冬天要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.75,0:35:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到了那時 莉茲要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.50,0:35:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哪裡都不去 就待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.88,0:35:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.59,0:35:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}按順序來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.67,0:36:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.97,0:36:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.58,0:36:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧冢同學
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.59,0:36:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.30,0:36:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以稍微 談一談嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.76,0:36:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好久沒見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.18,0:36:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼你知道我在這
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.68,0:36:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.48,0:36:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是劍崎同學告訴我你可能在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.52,0:36:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.44,0:37:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}決定的參賽曲真是美妙的曲子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.99,0:37:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這首曲子裡 長笛與雙簧管象徵著莉茲與青鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.75,0:37:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}第三樂章的輪流獨奏 一定是莉茲與少女的離別
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.51,0:37:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美 不是昨天停止活動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.13,0:37:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧冢同學不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.85,0:37:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.06,0:37:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不是很懂莉茲放走青鳥的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.40,0:37:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.95,0:37:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對了 今天來找你是有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.91,0:37:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧冢同學 你志願決定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.80,0:38:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.93,0:38:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.14,0:38:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.23,0:38:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.57,0:38:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在這做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.86,0:38:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}餵食給河豚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.49,0:38:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像莉茲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.00,0:38:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你很喜歡河豚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.13,0:38:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.09,0:38:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下次我也來餵可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.05,0:38:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.34,0:38:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.30,0:38:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小冊子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.10,0:38:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.18,0:38:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.81,0:39:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}音樂大學的手冊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.44,0:39:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 這個 霙要考音樂大學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.65,0:39:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新山老師給我的 說我會有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.75,0:39:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.00,0:39:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我就考這個大學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.17,0:39:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那 我也要考
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.10,0:39:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美想考的話 我也要考
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.69,0:39:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這日程的編制方法是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.78,0:39:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你一個人太胡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.95,0:39:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你這是來多管閒事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.36,0:39:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你可不是明日香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.66,0:39:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我知道 這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.75,0:40:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.34,0:40:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美 部費呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.97,0:40:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}冢本 瀧川和瀧野還沒交
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.59,0:40:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快去催催 快
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.68,0:40:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 要我去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.10,0:40:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}財務是你負責的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.35,0:40:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸 這天要模擬測驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.06,0:40:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}本來還想專心於部門活動
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.32,0:40:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}志願校跟我一樣 你也有可愛的地方的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.95,0:40:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊? 這點可簡直是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.12,0:40:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去了大學也一直是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.08,0:40:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說什麼呢 起雞皮疙瘩了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.12,0:40:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}內定的學校是一樣的也絕對是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.12,0:40:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好~好~
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.76,0:40:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙要考音樂大學
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.47,0:40:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣的嗎 霙很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.30,0:40:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.89,0:41:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為希美要考 所以我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.65,0:41:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們在當真什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.03,0:41:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是霙的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.86,0:41:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美要考音樂大學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.41,0:41:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大概吧 但是還不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.33,0:41:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.13,0:41:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}馬上要到縣祭典了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.67,0:41:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不妙 時間完全不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.80,0:41:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你還是先把社團這邊放一放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.05,0:41:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.81,0:41:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}縣祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.15,0:41:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸 你跟別人有約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.98,0:41:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.28,0:41:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.11,0:41:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美想去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}優子還有夏紀也沒約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.50,0:42:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 ok 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.88,0:42:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}部長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.30,0:42:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去倒是去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.92,0:42:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙呢 有想跟誰一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.55,0:42:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.77,0:42:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8\fs40}來氣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.83,0:42:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8\fs40}你那是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.30,0:42:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\an8\fs40}都說了是多管閒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.43,0:42:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.07,0:42:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希學姐 下次我們倆要去水族館了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.65,0:42:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}同個班級的嗎 真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.87,0:42:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要穿什麼去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.12,0:42:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這場合肯定要穿連衣裙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.24,0:42:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你沒有連衣裙吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.08,0:42:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.17,0:42:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我借你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.12,0:42:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 可以嗎 蕾學姐太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.17,0:42:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你穿得了蕾實的衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.18,0:43:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.68,0:43:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.56,0:43:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是不是叫「霙學姐」這樣不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.19,0:43:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}倒沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.58,0:43:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙學姐 這個真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.33,0:43:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}外面賣的都是白色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.84,0:43:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.80,0:43:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.51,0:43:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們關係果然真好呢 真羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.76,0:43:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙學姐 下次試音會之前還想辦一次雙簧樂器聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.60,0:43:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙學姐也偶爾過來一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.90,0:44:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算我去了大家也不會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.37,0:44:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才沒有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.45,0:44:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.71,0:44:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.96,0:44:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.71,0:44:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.84,0:44:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}退還日期已經過了一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.84,0:44:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可能還有其他的人也想借書
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.43,0:44:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}圖書館的書是大家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.14,0:44:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.64,0:44:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今後會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.48,0:44:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.23,0:44:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不帶那麼指責的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.03,0:44:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還書什麼的本來就很容易忘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.16,0:44:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想看莉茲的話 明明可以看我借到的那本
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.50,0:44:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那樣不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.92,0:45:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那樣就成轉借了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.71,0:45:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了 霙
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.67,0:45:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}圖書館的書不可以轉借給別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.14,0:45:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.28,0:45:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.83,0:45:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙學姐在自己製作簧片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.42,0:45:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一半是自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.29,0:45:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是用小刀削一削嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.13,0:45:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再繞繞線什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.26,0:45:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.10,0:45:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下次教你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.64,0:45:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.02,0:45:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真高興
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.11,0:46:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.62,0:46:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.08,0:46:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}試音會落選了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.84,0:46:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明想和學姐一起參賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.98,0:46:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快樂冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.86,0:46:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.02,0:46:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.28,0:46:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}剛剛你和我同時說了一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.82,0:46:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 說了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.53,0:46:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「肚子餓了 想吃甜點」
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.37,0:46:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就在那時
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.58,0:46:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}馬上就大喊快樂冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.71,0:47:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}先說出來的人可以被請吃冰淇淋的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.55,0:47:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 那就是我要請小綠吃冰淇淋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.93,0:47:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 多謝款待 小葉月
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.26,0:47:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 我都不知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.10,0:47:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.48,0:47:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}椅子放這可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.66,0:47:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}夏天到了 真想去玩水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.71,0:47:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙 下次假期你有約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.21,0:47:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.13,0:47:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.51,0:47:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那去泳池玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.05,0:47:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.43,0:47:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.62,0:48:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.94,0:48:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以邀請其他人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.82,0:48:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦 什麼 霙竟然會說這種話真難得
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.24,0:48:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以哦 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.47,0:48:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}泳池照片
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.59,0:48:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咿呀 好緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.39,0:48:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有好多學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.73,0:48:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過 真高興能邀請我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.15,0:48:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣就成了夏天的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.70,0:48:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}照片可以發給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.83,0:49:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明年我會加油的 比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.34,0:49:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 學姐能幫忙看看我的簧片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.92,0:50:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}傘木同學 你有在聽雙簧管的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.88,0:50:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你的聲音雖然不錯 但是有點帶感情過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.88,0:50:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個部分 最重要的是傾聽彼此的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.64,0:50:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你得輕輕地與鎧冢同學對話
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.64,0:50:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.10,0:50:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.60,0:50:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧冢同學
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.11,0:50:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這裡雙簧管和長笛的輪奏是極其重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.40,0:50:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}長笛的試探你也得要有所回應
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.70,0:51:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在音樂上 會有無法寫入樂譜的東西存在
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.95,0:51:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請細細體會樂譜空隙間流動的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.08,0:51:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}更多地放歌 做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.92,0:51:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.84,0:51:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在削嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.80,0:51:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小梨梨花的份
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.97,0:51:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.85,0:51:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙要考音樂大學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.77,0:51:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}優子會為我高興嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.19,0:51:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}當然 非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.32,0:51:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙的話絕對考得上
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.65,0:51:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.05,0:51:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.24,0:51:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美要考音樂大學所以你也考嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.71,0:51:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.63,0:51:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.01,0:52:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.72,0:52:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美決定的事就是我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.90,0:52:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.44,0:52:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}優子學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.19,0:52:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小號到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.07,0:52:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}ok 馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.28,0:52:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.09,0:52:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以說句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.79,0:52:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉 其實我一直很在意自由曲的雙簧管獨奏
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.92,0:52:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}學姐 你和希美學姐不契合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.18,0:52:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}高坂
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.89,0:52:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.06,0:52:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}學姐現在的聲音聽起來很受拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.27,0:52:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像是在故意抑制一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.86,0:53:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大概 你從沒想過希美學姐會配合自己
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.20,0:53:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}高坂
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.37,0:53:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.62,0:53:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對不起 我不是要為難學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.00,0:53:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是 我想聽學姐真正的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.55,0:53:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.64,0:53:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.52,0:53:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.94,0:53:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是的 希美沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.61,0:53:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}受拘束是因為 我沒能放跑青鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.12,0:53:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為 我不知道希美下次什麼時候會不見
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.20,0:53:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}離開我 通過我的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.04,0:53:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}解脫希美什麼的 我絕對做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.17,0:54:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.01,0:54:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是莉茲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.38,0:54:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會把青鳥一直囚禁下去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.10,0:54:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}夏紀 你要參加模擬測驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.60,0:54:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要的 最少參加三個
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.48,0:54:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.07,0:54:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就一個… 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.36,0:54:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們不是明明要去同一所大學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.74,0:54:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.75,0:54:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙說了些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.75,0:54:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.92,0:54:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是比方說 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.79,0:54:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}倒沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.80,0:54:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但她決定好了目標 有在努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.26,0:54:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是和希美進同一所大學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.09,0:54:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你不覺得霙對我有些冷淡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.55,0:54:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哪裡有了 沒這回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.93,0:54:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我高一的時候不是一度退出過社團活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.94,0:55:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然現在回顧起來是好久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.36,0:55:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但霙會不會現在還對這件事耿耿於懷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.86,0:55:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為霙不太把心中的想法清楚地表達出來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.37,0:55:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我實在是有些不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.62,0:55:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}獨奏那裡也有些合不到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.41,0:55:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.21,0:55:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你們兩個都是長笛和高音部的王牌 都很酷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.75,0:55:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.13,0:55:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我覺得 被莉茲放走的青鳥 如果還想再見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.89,0:55:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要再回來不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.93,0:55:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣一來 莉茲的決心不就白白浪費了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.90,0:55:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不過 這不就是Happy End了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.53,0:55:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}從今天開始 為了比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.15,0:55:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}橋本老師和新山老師也會暫時一起參加我們的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.62,0:55:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}高三和高二的同學 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.33,0:56:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}高一的同學是初次見面 我叫橋本
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.67,0:56:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會在這期間看著大家的練習 多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.86,0:56:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙 待會再練一下獨奏的部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.62,0:56:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}新山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.84,0:56:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.21,0:56:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}傘木同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.88,0:56:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今年木管樂器的指導也拜託老師您了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.80,0:56:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今年作為比賽成員參賽了啊 多多關照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.31,0:56:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.94,0:57:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其實…我準備報考音樂大學
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.81,0:57:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.57,0:57:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.28,0:57:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果合適的話 什麼都可以向我問哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.87,0:57:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.83,0:57:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.33,0:57:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.00,0:57:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這個在之前聽的時候我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.34,0:57:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雙簧管和長笛在銜接的地方 沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.14,0:57:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然後呢 強行把我們帶到那條河豚那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.19,0:57:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說想讓我們看看這條魚
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.69,0:57:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}說和我一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.99,0:57:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那條魚很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.20,0:57:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是是河豚耶
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.70,0:57:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可愛不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.99,0:57:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對吧 希美
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.16,0:58:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}欸 啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.66,0:58:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可能是指我我胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.00,0:58:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蕾學姐的衣服我果然穿不了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.09,0:58:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒關係啦 你這個樣子就夠可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.88,0:58:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.14,0:58:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哦 霙
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.76,0:58:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.56,0:58:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.94,0:58:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.48,0:58:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.90,0:58:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在生什麼氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.90,0:58:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.74,0:58:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那…可以和我做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.63,0:58:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下次吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.98,0:59:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼辦 第三樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.95,0:59:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果不能和霙合上的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.95,0:59:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.37,0:59:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}進展不順嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.42,0:59:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.58,0:59:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你和霙
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.34,0:59:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.67,0:59:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到正式演出為止還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.93,0:59:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在這之前總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.02,0:59:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 是小黃前他們
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.61,0:59:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這不是希美她們的獨奏部分嗎 她們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.42,1:00:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感覺就像是堅定的莉茲一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.38,1:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}分別的時候只會說一句「保重」
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.01,1:01:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}確實是高坂的風格
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.51,1:01:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.80,1:01:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我啊 是真的想要去音樂大學嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.36,1:01:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那個 我果然不是很懂獨奏
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.95,1:01:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧冢同學 你在這段獨奏中表達了什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.83,1:01:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲的感情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.46,1:01:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什麼樣的感情?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.63,1:01:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}將變得很要好的青鳥放出籠子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.34,1:01:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}給它自由
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.51,1:01:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是莉茲的行動 並不是感情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.94,1:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感情是…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.07,1:02:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.74,1:02:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為我做不到讓喜歡的人離開我
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.99,1:02:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有辦法理解 也不明白
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.46,1:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然喜歡長笛 但我真的想把它作為職業嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.67,1:02:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}當作工作和想要繼續演奏樂器又不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.34,1:02:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還有 很花錢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.26,1:02:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}畢竟得找老師一對一指導
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.47,1:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以我覺得 是不是像你們兩個一樣去普通的大學會比較好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.19,1:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這件事 霙知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.07,1:02:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.44,1:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼問這個?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.28,1:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你問為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.49,1:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}約好了一起去音樂大學
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.24,1:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}卻突然說什麼因為不想把它當職業所以不去了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.58,1:02:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.54,1:02:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}優子
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.21,1:03:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一年級的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.50,1:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你瞞著霙退出社團
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.34,1:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}結果又說想要參加然後跑了回來
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.85,1:03:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你到底要玩弄霙到什麼地步
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.97,1:03:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}優子
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.77,1:03:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算就在身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.39,1:03:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家也不是什麼事都會說吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.95,1:03:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鎧冢同學一定是對自己喜歡的人喜歡過頭的類型呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.50,1:03:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.29,1:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那麼 如果鎧冢同學是青鳥的話呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.96,1:03:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那一天莉茲突然與青鳥告別
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.35,1:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明之前一天 兩個人還幸福地生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.02,1:03:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你應該獲得自由
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.35,1:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你應該用那雙柔軟的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.15,1:04:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}展翅高飛到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.86,1:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.86,1:04:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想要和莉茲永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.91,1:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}與莉茲在一起我才會快樂
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.91,1:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是關住你的鳥籠
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.96,1:04:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你有你的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.42,1:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你還有那無限延伸的天空
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.93,1:04:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不能從你那裡奪去你的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.31,1:04:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}來吧 從這裡出去
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.40,1:04:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}向著遠方展翅高飛吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.36,1:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}請讓我看著你那美麗的身姿 為你送行
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.15,1:04:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就是我的愛的形式
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.62,1:05:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.31,1:05:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼樣? 青鳥飛出去了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.86,1:05:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是莉茲…莉茲這麼說了 所以青鳥才接受了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.86,1:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}青鳥無法阻止莉茲的選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.49,1:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為青鳥最喜歡莉茲了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.66,1:05:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即便傷心 也只能飛出去
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.25,1:05:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}青鳥是不幸的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.22,1:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.64,1:06:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是 莉茲希望她能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.81,1:06:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這一點一定是真心的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.27,1:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這就是青鳥的 愛的方式
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.11,1:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只能飛翔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.33,1:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}志願調查表 並不是只有霙什麼都沒填
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.58,1:06:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.88,1:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是 新山老師找的只有霙
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.05,1:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我一直想要把自己投影到莉茲身上
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.48,1:06:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲與青鳥她們啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.35,1:06:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我覺得很像我和霙
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.53,1:06:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙是…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.69,1:06:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}莉茲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.57,1:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.41,1:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}青鳥
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.49,1:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.80,1:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我因為過於喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.22,1:07:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以奪去了她美麗的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.39,1:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}她明明可以飛去任何地方的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.61,1:07:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}啊 神啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.73,1:07:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}為什麼要告訴我…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.78,1:07:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}打開鳥籠的方式呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.75,1:07:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}接下來 開始全體練習
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.13,1:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}首先是…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.00,1:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.59,1:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以練習一次第3樂章嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.64,1:08:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.17,1:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好厲害 學姐
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.55,1:12:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}攝人心魄
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.13,1:12:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都沒辦法集中精神演奏自己的部分了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.55,1:12:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙 真的非常棒
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.02,1:12:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.69,1:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.69,1:13:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.15,1:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.90,1:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.41,1:13:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.62,1:13:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在哭嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.12,1:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.33,1:13:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.79,1:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.80,1:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你至今為止都沒有拿出全力吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.60,1:13:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你為了配合我的水準
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.01,1:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以才一直沒使出全力吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.35,1:13:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.77,1:13:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.23,1:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}還對霙說什麼加油
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.07,1:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原來霙使不出全力 只是因為我的實力不足啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.99,1:13:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.53,1:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}畢竟被新山老師推薦去音樂大學的只有霙
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.91,1:14:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雖然我早就知道
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.54,1:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙在以前就很優秀了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.59,1:14:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙你太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.13,1:14:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.22,1:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.80,1:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不想輸給霙
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.35,1:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想著要和你對等
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.15,1:14:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以才說要和你一起去音樂大學
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.65,1:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為我沒有才能
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.19,1:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因為我不像你那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.91,1:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}覺得只要說「要去音樂大學」 就看起來會變得強一點
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.58,1:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.37,1:14:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我 不像霙一樣厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.97,1:14:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是普通人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.97,1:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.64,1:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙 你今後一定會前往更寬廣的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.77,1:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會為了配得上你的演奏 努力練習莉茲與青鳥的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.86,1:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.82,1:15:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我會為了能配合霙的獨奏而…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.86,1:15:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}聽我說
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.41,1:15:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美你總是這麼不顧及別人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.12,1:15:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一年級的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.04,1:15:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}擅自就退出了 還瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.13,1:15:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都是過去的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.47,1:15:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不是過去 對我來說一直都在眼前
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.72,1:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我一直在追隨著你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.85,1:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我不想被你丟下 才堅持著練習樂器
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.77,1:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你一直是我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.11,1:15:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想和你在一起 所以才努力練習雙簧管
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.03,1:16:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要能和希美在一起 怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.66,1:16:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}別說的這麼誇張…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.79,1:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}沒有誇張
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.75,1:16:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.63,1:16:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這麼說好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.21,1:16:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.64,1:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我並不是霙心目中的那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.31,1:16:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不如說 不值得你看得起
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.10,1:16:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美對我來說很特別
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.77,1:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算對你自己來說不值一提 你也是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.90,1:16:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我的全部 我的特別
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.95,1:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真搞不懂你為什麼那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.58,1:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.88,1:16:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「最喜歡了」的擁抱
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.78,1:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要是失去了希美 就一無所有了 也不會練習樂器
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.03,1:17:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你跟我搭話 成為我的朋友 溫柔地對待我
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.92,1:17:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我很開心
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.46,1:17:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}抱歉 我都記不清這些了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.38,1:17:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你帶領著大家 總是樂在其中的樣子 我覺得你很厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.31,1:17:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}霙是很努力的人哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.81,1:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我喜歡你的笑聲 喜歡你的言談
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.65,1:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喜歡你的腳步聲 喜歡你的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.61,1:18:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我喜歡你…你的全部
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.28,1:18:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我喜歡霙的雙簧管
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.11,1:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}希美?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.70,1:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.87,1:18:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝你 霙
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.17,1:18:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.01,1:19:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了 該回去了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.55,1:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我去拿東西
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.23,1:19:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是叫鎧冢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.20,1:19:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}參加社團了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.53,1:19:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就是放學回家的那種囉 什麼部都沒加入啊
