Comment: 0,1:28:09.18,1:28:16.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,The two lines come close and then get away.
Comment: 0,1:28:17.14,1:28:25.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Some easy tricks on Cat’s Cradle,That I can’t do so well any more.
Comment: 0,1:28:25.73,1:28:33.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,On a musical stave,Seasons pass so fast.
Comment: 0,1:28:34.20,1:28:42.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Each spring time,We’re floating there like balloons.
Comment: 0,1:28:42.42,1:28:50.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,The ghosts banished from my diary,Which I burnt in early summer.
Comment: 0,1:28:51.13,1:28:59.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,A rustling sound in the corridor,Somewhere in my heart.
Comment: 0,1:28:59.48,1:29:07.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Through the frosted window,If I was aware of the eyes behind the lens,
Comment: 0,1:29:07.98,1:29:11.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,How would I sing?
Comment: 0,1:29:11.99,1:29:20.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Golden reflections of our life,In the afternoon sunlight.
Comment: 0,1:29:20.50,1:29:24.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Chocolates melting in my pocket.
Comment: 0,1:29:24.50,1:29:28.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,By making it a song,Can I keep the memory?
Comment: 0,1:29:28.84,1:29:31.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,I just came to love it now.
Comment: 0,1:29:31.26,1:29:35.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,By making it a song,Can I keep the memory?
